Page Object Model for Acceptance Tests Design: 
 Page object model is one of the preferred test design pattern for UI tests. It helps in :
  - Encapsulation 
  - Increases test readability - Cleaner code
  - Separation of responsibilty
  - Refactoring tests becomes easier
  
  Links: 
  https://www.martinfowler.com/bliki/PageObject.html
